    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The scroll wasn't restored. I checked again, and it turns out it's the case only on CodeSandbox.\r\nIt works well both on my local machine and on Vercel: https://infinitehits-cache-m86tvb8nd.now.sh/\r\nWhen I tested on CodeSandbox, when I press back button to come back to the InstantSearch page, there were many CodeSandbox-related things that were loaded. It delayed the load of IS, and resulted no scroll restoration.\r\n\r\nSo it's ready for review!",
