    "body": "What you could do is an integration test that follows these steps:\r\n\r\n1. Add `infiniteHits({ cache: customCache })` where the custom cache implements the documented interface\r\n2. Search stuff...\r\n3. Go back to a previous state\r\n4. Make sure that the cache is read\r\n\r\nWould that make sense?",
